    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>God's Chosen Ministry was established on September 29th, 2019, in Nairobi, Kahawa West, Kamuthi. Led by PST. Chris Sila, our mission is to teach people the word of God and the power of prayer. Our vision is to be a mountain of deliverance and soul winning.</p>
    </section>

